config BR2_PACKAGE_AX25_APPS
	bool "ax25-apps"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBAX25
	select BR2_PACKAGE_NCURSES
	help
	  This package provides specific user applications for hamradio that
	  use AX.25 Net/ROM or ROSE network protocols:

	  - axcall: a general purpose AX.25, NET/ROM and ROSE connection program.
	  - axlisten: a network monitor of all AX.25 traffic heard by the system.
	  - ax25ipd: an RFC1226 compliant daemon which provides encapsulation of
	    AX.25 traffic over IP.
	  - ax25mond: retransmits data received from sockets into an AX.25
	    monitor socket.
